[h4 id=DisplayConfigurationAndFinalSettings 
	" Display configuration and final settings
	$LF
]h4
[div class=p 
	"After restarting, open the 
	[em 
		"Control Panel
	]em
	", open 
	[em 
		"Display
	]em
	", click on the 
	[em 
		"Settings
	]em
	" tab, change the 
	[em 
		"Color palette
	]em
	" to 
	[em 
		"True Color (32 bit)
	]em
	" and the 
	[em 
		"Desktop area
	]em
	" to 1024 by 768 pixels, then click 
	[em 
		"OK
	]em
	":
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	[img class=embed mw-100 src=https://files.tasvideos.org/common/Wiki/pcem/windows/configurations/Win95EmbiggenDisplay.png 
	]img
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"On the compatibility warning window, select 
	[em 
		"OK
	]em
	" to restart the computer with the new settings:
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	[img class=embed mw-100 src=https://files.tasvideos.org/common/Wiki/pcem/windows/configurations/Win95RestartDisplay.png 
	]img
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"When Windows reboots to the larger desktop size and color depth, close the 
	[em 
		"Control Panel
	]em
	", then shut down the computer:
